function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)

	-- Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_HELP, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_HELP, idActorPlayer, idDeadNPC)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idDyingMan = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idActorNPC, true)
	Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idDyingMan, sDying, sDead)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idDyingMan, 1)
	
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idDeadNPC, S_CONVO_HELP)
	-- Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_DyingVillagerCallOut, idSelf)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_DyingVillagerCallOut, idSelf, idDeadNPC)
end
